                Libero et <supplied reason="lost">Li</supplied>berae <lb n="2"/>pro sa<supplied reason="lost">lu</supplied>te <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et aete<supplied reason="lost">rni</supplied>tatis <note>sic</note> impe<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>ri</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> i<supplied reason="lost">n h</supplied><expan><abbr>onore</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Minic<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> Martialis <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">e(quo)</supplied> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex cert="low">ublico</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Minic</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Hermaisc</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei nicht aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. Maße beziehen sich auf das linke Fragment (a); Fragment b: (81,5) x 75,5) x 16,5 cm. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben.</p>
